data.description: Welcome to this exquisite home in The Villages at Riverdale Subdivision. Features include a remarkable 3rd-floor Smart Space room with breathtaking views. The residence is in like-new condition and situated on an end lot, filling every corner with natural light. The versatile third-floor space can serve as an office, children's play area, or entertainment haven. Three bedrooms and the laundry room are conveniently located on the second floor. The Primary Bedroom comes with a spacious walk-in closet. The lower level boasts an open layout connecting the Kitchen, Dining, and Living Room, perfect for social gatherings and day-to-day living. Outside, enjoy the recently constructed deck and low-maintenance turf, ideal for outdoor entertaining and summer barbecues. The Attached 2 Car Garage opens directly into the kitchen for easy grocery unloading. There's also a crawl space on the First Floor for extra storage. Don't miss this remarkable residence with stunning views, modern amenities, and a versatile floor plan, perfect for you and your loved ones.
